{"tid":487300,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人明明勁乾淨洗完頭都好多頭皮","createTime":"2017-12-02T15:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T16:15:29.000Z","uid":46020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"632f1aa79cc8a77b6af1d8b5c3a857960ac29b6d","tid":487300,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"隔日洗頭<br />\n每次都用溫水，唔會過熱或過冷<br />\n每次洗頭都會洗兩次（過完第一次泡再落洗頭水又洗一次）<br />\n每次都用護髮素（無搽落頭皮）<br />\n洗頭水唔會用死一隻，定期換<br />\n而家用緊日本牌子curel保濕洗頭水同埋獅王嘅去頭皮洗頭水<br />\n屌都係會有頭皮<br />\n<br />\n飲食平時都唔點食刺激類食物<br />\n都係十二點一點訓<br />\n<br />\n點先解決到？<br />\n有無巴絲過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efed2fc4ce5bc43be0e007ffef59b50a6c287b95","tid":487300,"uid":2155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"試下用防敏感"},{"pid":"d48e4c208383604c6744528f04f26b3d7f9ba1bf","tid":487300,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下用防敏感</blockquote><br />\n茶樹油果d"},{"pid":"ae6c0f95ff46747282243a2a7b91f7e423194236","tid":487300,"uid":124058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"我係hktv mall買左隻茶樹洗頭水 用完好返好多 不過頭髮好乾"},{"pid":"bbc87205ee73db5793d64cc95168ba7805559ffa","tid":487300,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"床單 枕頭<br />\n十二點算夜訓<br />\n壓力大？"},{"pid":"c3a382db21d6cb9acca005ca051adfe17c040b24","tid":487300,"uid":46020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>床單 枕頭<br />\n十二點算夜訓<br />\n壓力大？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔可以講無壓力但都無大到要有頭皮掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da355ec159a9844222cb36a2e91a677765b509a3","tid":487300,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"每日洗"},{"pid":"8a34f8ae074530a64a2b3865f4eb3322eeefeed3","tid":487300,"uid":127466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"如果你天生係敏感頭皮，洗兩次洗髮水咪出事攞。洗髮水本身就會刺激頭皮，你個頭唔係咁污穢既話，洗一次就夠。頭髮唔係咁乾燥，根本連護髮素都唔駛用。有時轉天氣，就有頭皮出現，壓力都會。"},{"pid":"3be06254bf873a23fc7f5fad350d00a03d42b0a7","tid":487300,"uid":20736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"壓力大<br />\n成日諗住頭皮問題自然就成日個心形住形住<br />\n<br />\n我之前都係咁<br />\n本身個排有野煩 壓力有啲大<br />\n後尾開始見到頭皮就好訝異<br />\n平時自己都算乾淨 起碼日日都實有沖涼<br />\n之後開始沖涼個陣洗多一兩次頭 但都係有頭皮<br />\n<br />\n結果我諗係壓力加上自己擔心頭皮問題搞到啲頭皮問題無好過<br />\n後尾索性唔去成日諗<br />\n慢慢就無了<br />\n都成三年前嘅事了<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}